{"tid":1448553,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:18:07.000Z","uid":26298,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c988083f6ec3ba2cf3553b88a419370ec9b9136c","tid":1448553,"uid":26298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:35:02.000Z","msg":"標題：<br />\n「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvL7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=27205bdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvL7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=fc1bb692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"13823c376d1f6d04a56db36936b94c4979bee20e","tid":1448553,"uid":137900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7e0e916e2a3bd4c61463a5fff5282a3ac513aa7f","tid":1448553,"uid":159290,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:53:08.000Z","msg":"何必呢"},{"pid":"ae7b3f61bd09974b30d3236f094a7549ccbea2a0","tid":1448553,"uid":140452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:54:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a47be4cb9c8353c25d642d7cbb2e7e5fd7fbf193","tid":1448553,"uid":143016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:09:42.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"31f6b876b12757f4b7e9a5e23142cd9f9026475f","tid":1448553